+-------------------+
|   User            |
+-------------------+
| user_id (PK)      |
| first_name        |
| last_name         |
| email (UNIQUE)    |
| password_hash     |
| phone_number      |
| role (ENUM)       |
| created_at        |
+-------------------+

+--------------------------+
|        Property          |
+--------------------------+
| property_id (PK, UUID)   |
| host_id (FK → User)      |
| name (VARCHAR, NOT NULL) |
| description (TEXT, NOT NULL) |
| location (VARCHAR, NOT NULL) |
| pricepernight (DECIMAL, NOT NULL) |
| created_at (TIMESTAMP, DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) |
| updated_at (TIMESTAMP, ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) |
+--------------------------+

key

host_id: References User.user_id — host who owns the property



 Booking Entity

+-----------------------------+
|          Booking            |
+-----------------------------+
| booking_id (PK, UUID)       |
| property_id (FK → Property) |
| user_id (FK → User)         |
| start_date (DATE, NOT NULL) |
| end_date (DATE, NOT NULL)   |
| total_price (DECIMAL, NOT NULL) |
| status (ENUM: pending, confirmed, canceled) |
| created_at (TIMESTAMP, DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) |
+-----------------------------+

Each booking links a user to a property

status must be one of the 3 valid values



 Payment Entity

+-------------------------------------+
|              Payment                |
+-------------------------------------+
| payment_id (PK, UUID)               |
| booking_id (FK → Booking)           |
| amount (DECIMAL, NOT NULL)          |
| payment_date (TIMESTAMP, DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) |
| payment_method (ENUM: credit_card, paypal, stripe) |
+-------------------------------------+

Every payment is linked to one booking (1:1)

payment_method is restricted to accepted methods



 Review Entity

+-------------------------------+
|           Review             |
+-------------------------------+
| review_id (PK, UUID)          |
| property_id (FK → Property)   |
| user_id (FK → User)           |
| rating (INTEGER, 1-5 ONLY)    |
| comment (TEXT, NOT NULL)      |
| created_at (TIMESTAMP, DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) |
+-------------------------------+

A user leaves a review for a property

rating must be between 1 and 5



 Message Entity

+-------------------------------+
|           Message             |
+-------------------------------+
| message_id (PK, UUID)         |
| sender_id (FK → User)         |
| recipient_id (FK → User)      |
| message_body (TEXT, NOT NULL) |
| sent_at (TIMESTAMP, DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) |
+-------------------------------+

A user can send messages to another user

Both sender_id and recipient_id reference the same User table
